110    public function testShouldParseXmlConfigurationRootAttributes(string $optionName, string $optionValue, bool|int|string $expected): void
111    {
112        $tmpFilename = sys_get_temp_dir() . DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR . 'phpunit.' . $optionName . uniqid('', true) . '.xml';
113        $xml         = "<phpunit {$optionName}='{$optionValue}'></phpunit>" . PHP_EOL;
114        file_put_contents($tmpFilename, $xml);
115
116        $configuration = (new Loader)->load($tmpFilename);
117
118        $this->assertFalse($configuration->hasValidationErrors());
119
120        $this->assertEquals($expected, $configuration->phpunit()->{$optionName}());
121
122        @unlink($tmpFilename);
123    }

141    public function testSourceConfigurationIsReadCorrectly(): void
142    {
143        $source = $this->configuration('configuration_codecoverage.xml')->source();
144
145        $this->assertTrue($source->hasBaseline());
146        $this->assertSame(realpath(__DIR__ . '/../../../../_files') . DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR . '.phpunit/baseline.xml', $source->baseline());
147
148        $directory = iterator_to_array($source->includeDirectories(), false)[0];
149
150        $this->assertSame('/path/to/files', $directory->path());
151        $this->assertSame('', $directory->prefix());
152        $this->assertSame('.php', $directory->suffix());
153
154        $file = iterator_to_array($source->includeFiles(), false)[0];
155        $this->assertSame('/path/to/file', $file->path());
156
157        $file = iterator_to_array($source->includeFiles(), false)[1];
158        $this->assertSame('/path/to/file', $file->path());
159
160        $directory = iterator_to_array($source->excludeDirectories(), false)[0];
161        $this->assertSame('/path/to/files', $directory->path());
162        $this->assertSame('', $directory->prefix());
163        $this->assertSame('.php', $directory->suffix());
164
165        $file = iterator_to_array($source->excludeFiles(), false)[0];
166        $this->assertSame('/path/to/file', $file->path());
167    }
